item.title: CVE-FE66-2023-003
item.description: Description Vulnerability Description Feiqi Interconnect - FE Corporate Operations Management Platform is a cloud workstation based on technologies such as cloud computing, intelligence, big data, the Internet of Things, and mobile internet. The FE Corporate Operations Management Platform V6.6 can bypass login authentication and enter the administrator interface.
